<div type="bibliography">
  <p>Edited from the original plates by N. Ramesan (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:Ramesan1988_01"/><citedRange unit="item">C</citedRange></bibl>), without facsimiles and without translation.<note>Although the grant was according to Ramesan found together with the <ref target="DHARMA_INSVengiCalukya00059.xml">Uccāṭi grant of Jayasiṁha I</ref> and the <ref target="DHARMA_INSVengiCalukya00060.xml">Cendaṟa grant of Jayasiṁha II</ref>, it is apparently not reported in <bibl><ptr target="bib:ARIE1997-1998"/></bibl> with those two sets.</note> The present edition by Dániel Balogh thus follows the published edition, silently correcting only obvious typos<note>The text of the edition is printed in Devanagari, but was apparently typeset from a Romanised manuscript, giving rise to mistakes such as @@@ <foreign>सिम्ह</foreign> instead of <foreign>सिंह</foreign>.</note> and offering suggestions for improvement in the apparatus.</p>
